Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.30,0:21:08.58,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord0}{\c&HEBC4EA&}現実逃避の脳内で
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.58,0:21:11.01,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord0}{\c&HFBF5B1&}安寧の夢むさぼって
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.01,0:21:15.67,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord0}{\c&HBEC1FD&}呑気な平和がいつまでも続くって信じきっている
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.67,0:21:20.23,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur4\bord4}{\3c&HD37427&}現在陳腐な常識も 平俗凡愚な限界も
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.23,0:21:25.00,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur4\bord4}{\3c&HAD034D&}「全くもって下らないね」なの言ってんのはいったいどいつ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.00,0:21:29.53,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur4\bord4}{\3c&H1D2049&}かすれてく記憶の彼方で
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.53,0:21:34.33,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur4\bord4}{\3c&H1D2049&}ねじ曲げられてく 遥かな約束
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.33,0:21:38.89,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur4\bord4}{\3c&H85880C&}誰も皆忘れているなら
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.89,0:21:45.22,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur4\bord4\fs40\pos(655,1000)}{\3c&H85880C&}まなこ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.89,0:21:45.22,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur4\bord4}{\3c&H85880C&}眼を開いて 思い出させてやる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.38,0:21:50.14,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur4\bord4}{\3c&HAD034D&}超えてゆくのさ 残酷な世界を
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.14,0:21:54.68,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur4\bord4}{\3c&H2676F9&}誓い合ったあの日の儚い希望
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.68,0:21:59.45,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur4\bord4}{\3c&HD37427&}蹴り上げてやれ キミの痛みを
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.45,0:22:04.04,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur4\bord4}{\3c&HFE2EB8&}全てを飲み込むその業火で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.04,0:22:08.77,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur4\bord4}{\3c&HFE2EB8&}正解不正解 可能不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.77,0:22:15.38,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur4\bord4}{\3c&HFE2EB8&}全ては この手の中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.30,0:21:08.58,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord0}{\c&HEBC4EA&}在逃避現實的腦中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.58,0:21:11.01,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord0}{\c&HFBF5B1&}做著貪圖安寧的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.01,0:21:15.67,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord0}{\c&HBEC1FD&}堅信無憂無慮的和平會永遠持續下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.67,0:21:20.23,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur4\bord4}{\3c&HD37427&}現在那陳舊的常識 平凡庸俗的界限
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.23,0:21:25.00,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur4\bord4}{\3c&HAD034D&}「真拿你沒辦法啊」你到底在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.00,0:21:29.53,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur4\bord4}{\3c&H1D2049&}在模糊記憶的彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.53,0:21:34.33,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur4\bord4}{\3c&H1D2049&}被扭曲的遙遠約定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.33,0:21:38.89,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur4\bord4}{\3c&H85880C&}若把每一個人都忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.89,0:21:45.22,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur4\bord4}{\3c&H85880C&}就睜開雙眼 讓我回想起來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.38,0:21:50.14,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur4\bord4}{\3c&HAD034D&}互相起誓的那天虛假的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.14,0:21:54.68,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur4\bord4}{\3c&H2676F9&}跨越這個殘酷的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.68,0:21:59.45,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur4\bord4}{\3c&HD37427&}就用吞噬一切的業火
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.45,0:22:04.04,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur4\bord4}{\3c&HFE2EB8&}將你的痛楚一腳踢開
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.04,0:22:08.77,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur4\bord4}{\3c&HFE2EB8&}正確與錯誤 可能與不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.77,0:22:15.38,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur4\bord4}{\3c&HFE2EB8&}全都掌握於手中
